description:
Pose is the place to celebrate & shop unique style. Join our diverse and creative community in exchanging fashion inspiration and products that are as one-of-a-kind as you are. 

- The Pose community posts pictures of what they are wearing. Share your outfit or get inspired by the world’s largest community of fashion bloggers, stylists and celebs!

 - Ready to shop? Open the app and enter our vibrant marketplace where you can snag new, pre-owned and vintage pieces straight from the stylish closets of our Pose members.

- List your own items and unlock the value sitting in your closet.

- Upgrade your wardrobe by trading items with other members. Trade what you already have for what you love! 

From media and styling mogul Rachel Zoe, to blogger wunderkind the Man Repeller, to supermodel-turned-digital powerhouse Coco Rocha, to Girl With Curves: Our community acts as a reminder that we come in all shapes, sizes and colors, but the insides are all the same. We are one in our desire to reinvent ourselves every time that we get dressed. So, tell us: “who do you want to be today?” We’re listening.
releaseNotes:
Pose has a new look and an exciting new way to shop what you love.

- Get inspired by the new redesign, featuring a new Pose of the Day, every day!

- Apple Pay has come to Pose! If you find an item you love, it's only one touch away from being yours.

- Dive right into what interests you and what trends are being posed. We'll feature new collections each day, and we've made it easier to jump in and shop or just keep browsing poses.

- Improved look for iphone 6 and 6+.  

We hope you love the new updates and give us lots of love! We'll be jumping in and loving all your poses, too!

Don't forget! We want to hear from you! If there is something you love about the app, something you would change or a feature you're dying to have - let us know by emailing us at hello@pose.com or reaching out on Twitter @pose. We can't wait to chat with you about the new app!
